data.description:
PRICED TO SELL! WELCOME HOME ~SPACE for everyone! WELL KEPT~ Great size rooms. Primary bedroom 23x14 No carpet, renovated less than 3 years ago and some 2023. Never flooded X flood zone. Acre on a corner lot. Great access to I-55 and I-12. LOTS of storage. Circle driveway. Newer central heat, metal roof, floors, insulated windows with blinds and more. This is a must see. Pictures don't do justice.
Start now and be home for the holidays! Above ground pool is 1 yr. old 32x16x52 (4ft) for lots of summer cooling off.  Can stay with accepted offer. Seller is motivated and will consider all reasonable offers.
